abstract: Havre de Grace is likely morning-line favorite for the Classic, Breeder's Cup main event.
snippet: Havre de Grace has won five of her six starts this year, including an impressive victory in the Woodward Stakes.
lead_paragraph: Havre de Grace has won five of her six starts this year, including an impressive victory in the Woodward Stakes.
